56:35.618 --> 56:39.164
that something very similar seemed to happen in science fiction. Until the last few years I understand sex has been 
strikingly absent from science fiction, and there too has fairly recently, that isn't the last decade, made a

56:40.286 --> 56:50.525
comeback. Someone might be able to put me right on that point, but it's what I've gathered from my recent reading. I think 
