that is, to get their work published except as children's literature. So, fantasists, no matter how good, were forced

01:05:07.604 --> 01:05:12.891
to write for children. A realistic writer's work could get published as an adult book, even if it concerned a child or an 
adolescent, like a book like The Catcher in the Rye is a case in point. But a fantasist could not. And on the other hand,

01:05:27.911 --> 01:05:38.845
it's also true that fantasy was so despised that one could get away with a great deal by writing in fantasy which one could 
not get away with in realism for children. So a writer who wanted to write for children would be likely to turn to fantasy

01:05:39.382 --> 01:05:49.117
to escape the cramping restrictions placed on pseudo realism for children.

01:05:51.921 --> 01:06:02.537
